# cat focus: type command, show output, clear, repeat
Output assets/focus.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 420
Set Height 280
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show

Type "cat focus"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 600ms

Type "cat focus"
Enter
Sleep 3s
